lessonList.name: 全校
lessonList.courseName: 几何拓扑及高阶Teichmüller理论选讲
lessonList.remark:
We introduce the advanced topics on the (higher) Teichmuller theory by starting from the very beginning. The first two topics are:
1) We start from Riemann/hyperbolic surface, Teichmuller space, moduli space. Then we introduce the Mirzakhani's integration on the volume of the moduli space and related topics.
2) Fock--Goncharov duality and higher geodesic measure lamination from webs. We start from introducing geodesic measure lamination on Riemann surface and the surface group representations.
